text: Esther Domínguez (April 23, 1981, Zaragoza, Province of Zaragoza) is a Spanish rhythmic gymnast. Dominguez competed for Spain in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney.
